thread.title: Kalie

author: Kalie
title: Kalie
text:
I have been a member for over a year now, and I truly enjoy the pieces offered. I have done a variety of workouts over the last year and currently partake in Crossfit. I use fabletics items when I do the crossfit wardrobe malfunctions. I think the products are great quality and I can't get over the styles.
My only compliant is more or less disappointment that the outfits go so quick. It has become harder to get a hold of my top picks online. At the same time, this demonstrates how great the clothing is if it going this fast.
